## Step 6.3 — AI synthesis
**Status:** ✅ Completed
**Jira:** KAN-9
**File:** `lib/ai/synthesize-report.ts`

Single Claude Sonnet 4.6 call that takes tool context + `AllScrapeResults` and returns a typed `SynthesizedReport` covering all 10 sections. Prompt instructs the model to weight real scraped posts heavily when present and fall back to general knowledge when a source is empty. Retries once on JSON parse failure. Pros/cons capped at 5 items each in post-processing.

